    public abstract class XmlHandler<H extends XmlHandler<H,C,T,S>,C extends Connection,T extends XmlEvent<T,?,S>,S extends Enum<S>>
extends AbstractFilteredHandler<H,C,T>
implements Source<T,S>, FilterFactory<Filter<T,Element>,T,Element,H>
    A null-terminated packet protocol for reading and writing XmlEvents. Programmers will have to implement parse(Element) for system-specific behavior.
